            <title>[THRIFT-3040] bower.json wrong &quot;main&quot; path</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-3040</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;How to produce:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;bower install thrift -save&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;grunt wiredep&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;with the current path thrift is not included.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;it has to be changed from&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&quot;main&quot;: &quot;lib/js/thrift.js&quot;,&lt;br/&gt;
to&lt;br/&gt;
+  &quot;main&quot;: &quot;lib/js/src/thrift.js&quot;,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;



&lt;p&gt;Pull request on GitHub: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/thrift/pull/398&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/thrift/pull/398&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
